snippet.title: Atari ST Longplay: Liberator
snippet.description: Send your flying jacuzzi to rescue five Chinese blokes caged-up in five weird worlds, while zapping the robots/monsters on the way. Save-states used. Just liberate me from the monotonous music. No, this isn't bad for something a bunch of teenagers might have made. Pity there's no ending after all that struggle.
